{"tid":805730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稅務局出手！江蘇常州一企業被追徵十年的社保","createTime":"2018-09-04T05:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T11:31:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac19fd3bbe163bdc8ff13620e4fa0fb13c0ba0f","tid":805730,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"據江蘇省常州市新北區人民法院8月23日發佈的行政裁定書顯示，常州市柏華玻璃有限公司2007年12月至2017年11月期間欠繳基本養老保險費、基本醫療保險費、工傷保險費、失業保險費、生育保險費合計2011134.15元，根據《社會保險法》和《江蘇省社會保險費徵繳暫行條例》的規定，江蘇省常州地方稅務局第五稅務分局作出社會保險費徵收決定，對格華玻璃公司徵收社會保險費。在徵收對定生效後，因該公司未全部履行繳納義務，稅務機關向法院申請強制執行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.guancha.cn/politics/2018_09_03_470583.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.guancha.cn%2Fpolitics%2F2018_09_03_470583.shtml&d=AE7adLJ16%2Bv8t4P6ZbmGqtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=5b5d4ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.guancha.cn/politics/2018_09_03_470583.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"0d4c407b02dd1d4ee998049afcb040456125f5b0","tid":805730,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WM08i2T_kwM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWM08i2T_kwM&d=AE7adLJ16%2Bv8t4P6ZbmGqtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bf36945f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WM08i2T_kwM</a><br />\n<br />\n好正"},{"pid":"b278d605136356a054843de277e183dc73da7815","tid":805730,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:31:12.000Z","msg":"諗起琴日有條5毛自稱自己做中國研究讀緊MASTER,狂吹5險1金"}]}